Package com.arjuna.mw.wscf.exceptions

Exception Summary
BegunFailedException The coordination protocol failed to start.
DuplicateParticipantException There was an attempt to register the same participant with the coordinator.
InvalidParticipantException The specified participant is invalid in the context used.
NoCoordinatorException There is no coordinator associated with the target.
ProtocolAlreadyRegisteredException An attempt has been made to register the same coordination protocol with the protocol factory.
ProtocolNotRegisteredException An attempt was made to act on a protocol that the protocol factory had no knowledge of.
UnexpectedException A general error has occurred.
UnknownProtocolImplementationException An attempt was made to operate on a protocol implementation that the factory did not know about.
UnsupportedQualifierException Exception reported if a given qualifier is not supported.
